message: We are super excited about this wonderful opportunity. The Neely Agency, LLC is having their mixer on Sun Jan 21, 2017, in Memphis, TN. The event includes Networking, Mini Fashion Show, Taping of Cable Show, and a Panel Discussion with our very own Kelley Alsobrook. Proceeds from the event will benefit our programs. They are working to raise awareness by holding this event during National Human Trafficking and Slavery Prevention Month.  Please see the flyer for all the details. #Grateful
